.el .IP "\fI\f(CI$c_set\fI\fR = \f(CWcomplement\fR \fI\f(CI$set\fI\fR" 4
.IX Item "$c_set = complement $set"
Returns the set of integers that are not in \fI\f(CI$set\fI\fR.
